Package com.craws.mrx.state

Class Timeline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.craws.mrx.state.Timeline
  • public class Timeline
extends java.lang.Object
    The Timeline-class manages the timeline keeping track of the moves of Mr. X. The Tickets will be associated with the Place they were used to visit. The entries work as follows: [Index] | Ticket | Place [0] | null | StartPosition Mr. X [1] | 1st Ticket used | Position after 1st Ticket used [x] | x-th Ticket used | Position after x-th Ticket used
